957
00:49:51,010 --> 00:49:51,999
Eso podría ser agresivo- -

958
00:49:52,077 --> 00:49:53,135
¿Podemos procesarlos a ellos?

959
00:49:55,514 --> 00:49:56,742
Me di cuenta

960
00:49:56,815 --> 00:49:59,511
